'''Aarwynn''' was a huge [[humbaba]] and was known as the [[Kashoonara]] legend as the steed of the deity [[Hurrungat]]. The legend said that Aarwynn was "six Kashoonara high" at the shoulder, which was much larger than the real humbaba.<ref name="CotG">''[[Creatures of the Galaxy]]''</ref>

